3.00	USS_Pledge_(AM-277)	USS Pledge (AM-277)	USS Pledge (AM-277) was an Admirable-class minesweeper built for the U.S. Navy during World War II. She was built to clear minefields in offshore waters, and served the Navy in the Atlantic Ocean and then was transferred to the North Pacific Ocean. She survived the world war and was awarded one battle star, but, during the Korean War, she struck a mine and was sunk. She received the Presidential Unit Citation for her Korean service.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/01/USSPirate%26otherAdmirableClassMinesweeper.jpg/300px-USSPirate%26otherAdmirableClassMinesweeper.jpg
